thread.title_full: California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance reviewed by Camille Hudson

author: Camille Hudson
title: Camille Hudson
text: I would have given California Casualty a 5 star review but it is not available in North Carolina. But they helped me change to Progressive. My dealings with California Casualty were efficient and helpful. I would highly recommend them.
